parameters: Are you excited for your big event Violet?!
Yup, there's a lot of fresh talent out there today.
My girls are salivating at the thought of servicing a new champion.
That is-\! assuming a winner even emerges from those beasts.
I'm confident they'll be far too much for any single competitor to take on.
I wouldn't be so sure this time.
There's a new entrant who is drawing my attention.
He claims to reside from outside the city.
I'm not sure how that's even possible currently...
There's no way that could happen unless...
Whatever, I wouldn't sweat it.\! He's probably just lying to generate excitement.
Hmm, I suppose it won't matter.
Say, there's still one more spot open.
Are you sure you don't want to sign up Norman?
And get blood on my new suit?!\! Oh heavens no!
Regardless, my girls would love to show you some hospitality later.
I'm.. afraid I'll have to decline, thank you very much.
I believe I'm late for another important meeting.
I'll be on my way Violet.
Might I suggest replacing your guards.\! They seem to be getting quite careless...
Did you find anything useful over there?
We found a generator.\! Supposedly, it's what's causing people to turn into zombies.
You knew?!\! Tell me, what all do you know about the generator?
That asshole Reeves has been using it against me as a bargaining chip!
He demanded my cooperation, in exchange for keeping the Underground
But if I were to disobey...
He's threatening to turn everyone here into zombies?!
He is.\! I didn't believe him at first.
But then he set off a generator above ground.
I saw the horrors that occurred in that area!
Instantly, I knew I was powerless to do anything about it...
That must be the generator that caused the zombies near us, Lucy.
All he has to do is set off that nearby generator and all of the men here turn into monsters.
Everything I've worked for could be erased in an instant...
Not a minute goes by that I don't worry about that threat.
People think I'm in this position because of the money, or for the fame.
But the Underground and it's people mean everything to me.
I can't bear to lose that...
We won't let him do that.
Yeah, we'll find a way to stop him!
I warned you \n[1].\! You're picking a fight with a sick, twisted man.
He's hurt so many people Violet.\! Innocent people.
It-\! It makes my hands shake with anger!
I could never let him get away with this!
You know, I didn't think I'd ever believe anyone had the power to stop him.
But you might just be crazy enough to do it!
If the time comes, you have the support of myself and the citizens of the Underground.
That is very kind of you Violet.
Thank you for your time.\! We'll be on our way now.
So what do you think our next step is, Lucy?
We'll come up with a plan of action after we get some rest.
The performance out there has been quite a sight to behold!
Quite a lot of talent today, isn't there?
My girls and I have been glued to our seats.
Maybe he can draw in an attendance boost to The Underground.
It's truly a shame the state this district is in...
It's just one disaster away from being put out of it's misery.
Aha ha!\! \BST[1]No need for hostilities my dear Violet.
As long as you continue to cooperate, there's no need to worry.
Well look at the time!\! I believe I'm late for another important meeting.
I'll be on my way Violet.
Might I suggest replacing your guards.\! They seem to be getting quite careless...
